thread.title_full: Custom Automotive reviewed by Greg Wodack

author: Greg Wodack
title: Greg Wodack
text:
I highly recommend Custom Automotive. The customer service and advice is outstanding. Dustin Brown is a wealth of knowledge. I am a business owner myself and Custom Automotive possess all the qualities necessary to make a successful company. Great personalized customer service, speedy delivery of their product, My new wheels and tires arrived safely and without incident and I love them, exactly what I wanted.
Greg W.
Viginia
